{
    "name": "Soulbound Doll",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "These small, sentient dolls contain a fragment of another creature\u2019s soul. The binding process strips most of the individuality from the soul, making a new soulbound doll an almost blank slate. Despite this process, fragments of the original creature\u2019s personality remain.<br/><br/>Soulbound dolls can serve as companions, surrogate children, servants, guards, and sentries, as desired by their creators. Creators of soulbound dolls typically take care to take soul fragments from people whose personality traits the crafters wish to see in their dolls."
        }
    ],
    "html": "<i>This doll\u2019s glass eyes glisten with unmistakable curiosity as it comes to life with a fluid grace.</i>",
